@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Help";
}

@section Styles {
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/Help.css" />
}

<div class="help-container">
    <h1>📘 ManagerApp — User Guide</h1>
    <p class="intro-text">
        Welcome to the documentation page! Here you’ll find descriptions of each major section of the <strong>ManagerApp</strong>, along with their purpose and usage. This guide will help you quickly understand how to navigate and use the system efficiently.
    </p>

    <section>
        <h2>🏠 Dashboard</h2>
        <p>The central hub of the application. Displays key performance indicators, recent activities, and system status. Ideal for quick overviews and daily checks.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>📦 Orders</h2>
        <p>This section allows you to manage all customer or internal orders. You can create new orders, edit existing ones, view statuses, and track progress.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>📐 BTU Calculator</h2>
        <p>An integrated tool that calculates the necessary cooling capacity (in BTUs) based on input parameters such as room size. Helps recommend suitable AC models for customer needs.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>❄️ Search Conditioners</h2>
        <p>A searchable and filterable list of available air conditioners. Filter by BTU, brand, price, area served, and other parameters to find the best match for your clients.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>🏬 Warehouses</h2>
        <p>Manage all warehouse-related operations. You can view, edit, or remove warehouses, as well as track stocks of equipment, tools, and materials by category.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>🗺️ Navigation</h2>
        <p>Access real-time warehouse locations through an interactive map (powered by MapLibre). Useful for route planning or locating resources quickly.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>⚙️ Settings</h2>
        <p>Manage your preferences — from language and UI themes to security settings and personal information. A must-visit for customizing your experience.</p>
    </section>
</div>
